name: ZetaChain Bridged ETH.BASE (ZetaChain)
description: ZetaChain bridged ETH.base on ZetaChain is a wrapped and bridged version of native ETH held in our Base custody address. Users deposit native ETH from Base in our custody address, secured by MPC TSS. The protocol then issues a wrapped version equivalent, ZRC-20 on ZetaChain that be natively withdrawn back to the source chain or used in the ecosystem. Please see link below for liquidity caps and other token information: https://explorer.zetachain.com/liquidity
